22-yard game-winning field goal with 4:41 left to play to lift Menlo (1-4) to a 
22-21 victory over Redlands (2-1-1) at Menlo. The victory snapped Menlo's 
18-game winless streak. . . . Antonio Warren rushed for 83 yards and a 
touchdown to lead Cal Poly San Luis Obispo (2-3) to a 35-30 victory over host 
San Francisco State (2-4). 
