<TEXT>
<P>
 Wrong district -- Biographical information published Saturday about Republican 
Assemblyman Nao Takasugi and Democratic challenger Dorothy Maron incorrectly 
reported the district they are seeking to represent. They are running for the 
37th Assembly District. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
